<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The current implementation of Zend_Db_Table_Row throws an exception when attempting to set the value of the primary key. This is annoying when importing records with pre-existing id's.  Suggest that we allow setting the id when it's current value is null.</p>

    </div>
